		<RichText x="66" y="698" width="509" height="97" kerning="off" blendMode="normal" whiteSpaceCollapse="preserve" alpha="0.9019607843137255">
			<content>
				<p fontFamily="仓耳渔阳体 W03" fontSize="16" fontWeight="bold" color="#ffffff">凛狼在战斗中召唤的冰狼魂，拥有<span color="#99ffff">12冻</span><span>盾，可以被选中瞄准，但仅能被</span><span color="#ffacff">雷扩散</span><span>与</span><span color="#ff9999">火扩散</span><span>命中。狼魂的攻击力为凛狼的</span><span color="#ffbfbf">5/8</span><span>。凛狼与狼魂共存时，自身</span><span color="#ffdfbf">全抗+100%</span><span>。<br/></span><span color="#ffbfbf">(N5) </span><span>冰狼魂的厚度提升至</span><span color="#99ffff">24冻</span><span>盾，且凛狼与狼魂共存时，改为开启</span><span textDecoration="underline">风息屏障</span><span>而不提升抗性。</span></p>
			</content>
		</RichText>
